NAME
    App::Mver - just print modules' $VERSION

DESCRIPTION
    For those, who are sick of

        perl -MLong::Module::Name -le'print Long::Module::Name->VERSION'

SYNOPSIS
        mver Module::Name

        mver Module-Name

AUTHOR
    Алексей Суриков <ksuri@cpan.org>

